name: Daniel Rey Cimafranca
text: Yup dapat i carve out na yang infra.  Anti trust like what happened to AT&T.  Para isa na lang kausap tungkol dyan, pati sa national broadband, pati sa coverage ng picos machines during elections, to make it more viable for Google et al to create mirror servers here (internet becomes more costly if difference between inbound and outbound traffic is huge ), etc.
